data.meta_description: Watch Official Trailer for Clerks III Movie. Starring Cast Members Kevin Smith, Jay Mewes, Rosario Dawson. Directed by Kevin Smith. Coming out soon. Watch this comedy film, following a massive heart attack, Randal enlists Dante, Elias, Jay and Silent Bob to make a movie about the convenience store that started it all.
